short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Scrape members info from Telegram groups/channels (Pure js/no API/no behind the scenes activities)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Scrape members info (Name, Username, Bio, etc.) from Telegram "Groups/Channels"

Super Easy:
1.Open a Group/Channel in Telegram Web
2.Open Member List section
3.Click on the extension start button
-> All members info will be extracted and will be saved into your Downloads folder as a TXT file.

Completely FREE

A small part of Telegram Auto Activities Package (from v-User)
v-user.com/telegram
